# Amazon Sales Dashboard

## Objective
Built an interactive Excel dashboard to analyze sales performance across cities, states, and product categories.

## Tools Used
* Microsoft Excel
* Pivot Tables
* Pivot Charts
* Data Cleaning
* KPI Cards

## Dashboard Highlights
* Total Sales tracking
* Units sold analysis
* City-wise sales trends
* State-wise performance comparison
* Product-wise sales funnel

## Key Insights
* Identified high-performing cities and states
* Compared product contribution to overall sales
* Summarized business KPIs for quick decision-making
